CONTRIBUTION NOTES
------------------
See https://github.com/asgrim/godeploy/wiki/Contributing-to-GoDeploy for latest version of this document

See https://github.com/asgrim/godeploy/wiki/Requirements for latest requirements

We recommend using git-flow for your fork.
See: https://github.com/nvie/gitflow

REQUIREMENTS
------------
Linux, PHP 5.3.2, MySQL, php5_mcrypt, php5_ftp, git, openssh
We recommend Ubuntu Server 10.04 LTS.
Disable PHP safe mode, ensure Suhosin is permissive.

FORKING AND INSTALLING
----------------------
1. Fork https://github.com/asgrim/godeploy on GitHub
2. git clone git@github.com:[YOURUSER]/godeploy.git
2. cd library
3. git clone git://github.com/asgrim/mal.git MAL
4. svn co --quiet http://framework.zend.com/svn/framework/standard/tags/release-1.10.8/library/Zend Zend
5. cd ..
6. mkdir gitcache
7. chgrp -R www-data godeploy
8. chmod 775 gitcache
9. chmod 775 application/configs
10. Run setup script

UPDATING IN THE FUTURE
----------------------
1. git remote add upstream git://github.com/asgrim/godeploy.git
2. git fetch upstream
3. git merge upstream/develop

